Code:

Simply run frame_capture.py to obtain result images
feature_track.py has estimateAllTranslation, estimateFeatureTranslation, and applyGeometricTransformation functions. In get_features.py, we uses cv.goodFeaturesToTrack to extract feature points for the first frame. We have also included helper functions such as rgb2gray, interp2, drawpoints, and etc. in helpers.py.

